Dialogue: 9,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end it would seem Fukube Satoshi is a man of no talents.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:42.34,0:03:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that great talents bloom late, but that's rather unlikely at this point.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a database. What's to complain about?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:48.63,0:03:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do take some pride in how much I know,
Dialogue: 9,0:03:52.48,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even at my best I still wouldn't even qualify for "Quiz King" or anything.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really makes me jealous of people like that.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not all flowers and sunshine for them.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:04.90,0:04:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geniuses can't choose to live normal lives like ours, even if they wanted to.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is a normal life something that you wish for, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see how you might.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:18.09,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really think you'll be able to live one?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask, I would say Fukube Satoshi has no talents.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:27.41,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for Oreki Houtarou, I think I'll withhold any comments.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:33.34,0:04:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think I'm not a normal person then you have terrible observational skills.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying that I'm withholding my opinion on you for now.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, shouldn't we hurry up?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka will get mad if we're late to the meeting.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:48.37,0:04:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. It's our {\i1}summer break{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.10,aaaaa,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fs50\b\c&H42514F&\pos(988.486,367.171)}IN THE {\c&H525FBB&}FINALS{\c&H43524F&}!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:51.09,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go trying to play it off again!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Chitanda?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still not here...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit worried.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the difference in treatment here?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the difference in how you live your lives.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A preview screening!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the screening!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:12.61,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2-F is going to show a movie they made.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:17.43,0:05:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An acquaintance of mine in that class wants to hear our opinion.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:22.05,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Discussing it with her took more time than I thought.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of movie is it?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mystery movie, apparently.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:29.67,0:05:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.85,Staff Room,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fs35\pos(627.378,168.946)\i0\b1\c&H304141&}Audio Visual Classroom{\i1\b0}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be here.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, as promised!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your taking the time to assist us.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:49.86,0:05:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ibara Mayaka-san, Fukube Satoshi-san, and Oreki Houtarou-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:54.32,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all members of the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Irisu Fuyumi.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so! Irisu-senpai!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I'd seen you before!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:05.65,0:06:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't remember you.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you at the Cultural Festival Committee Meeting in June.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:11.34,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was amazed at how well you handled the dispute between the Light Music Club and the Drama Club.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to see Satoshi hold anyone in such high regard...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I don't recall.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:21.72,0:06:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know her, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family has known hers for a long time.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She helped me out a lot when I was younger.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be tough being part of a distinguished old family.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:34.03,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the movie that our class made.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:37.04,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to watch it and give your honest opinion of it.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want us to watch it and tell you what we think?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:48.46,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:50.85,0:06:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we don't like it, it's not like you're going to redo the whole thing.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just trying to get us to advertise it?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:57.21,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't understand why you want us to watch it.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A valid question.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:03.58,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are correct in that there would be no point in simply having you watch it.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:07.00,0:07:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe it would be more efficient for you to just watch it for now.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:11.17,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Efficient, huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This movie has yet to be titled.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're calling it "Mystery" for now.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:22.83,0:07:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're finished, I have a question I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will start shortly.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:37.75,0:07:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several volunteers from class 2-F decided to produce an exhibit on the history of Narakubo at the Kanya Festival.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:41.83,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went there as part of their research into it.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we there yet?
