Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.78,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&FF&\bord2\blur1\fs70\c&H282D26&\b0\3c&HA5B1AF&\pos(640,556.4)}Yamanishi Midori{\b1}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.53,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fs70\pos(640,556.4)\c&H282D26&}Sugimura Jirou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.53,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&FF&\bord2\blur1\fs70\c&H282D26&\b0\3c&HA5B1AF&\pos(640,556.4)}Sugimura Jirou
Dialogue: 9,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't be five minutes.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:53.92,0:07:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said that five minutes ago!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.53,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fs70\pos(640,556.4)\c&H212833&}Senoue Mamiko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.53,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&FF&\bord2\blur1\fs70\c&H282D26&\b0\3c&HA5B1AF&\pos(640,556.4)}Senoue Mamiko
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.54,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fs70\pos(640,556.4)\c&H1B1F21&}Kounosu Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.54,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&FF&\bord2\blur1\fs70\c&H1B1F21&\b0\3c&HA5B1AF&\pos(640,556.4)}Kounosu Yuri
Dialogue: 9,0:07:59.39,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a tough walk.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.00,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fs70\pos(640,556.4)\c&H343541&}Katsuta Takeo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.00,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&FF&\bord2\blur1\fs70\c&H1B1F21&\b0\3c&HA5B1AF&\pos(640,556.4)}Katsuta Takeo
Dialogue: 9,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, and I'm tired.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.04,0:08:09.88,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fs70\pos(640,556.4)\c&H343033&}Kaitou Takeo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:09.88,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&FF&\bord2\blur1\fs70\c&H1B1F21&\b0\3c&HA5B1AF&\pos(640,556.4)}Kaitou Takeo
Dialogue: 9,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't really expect more out of an independent film.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see it now.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Narakubo over there.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. It looks like a good place to research.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a place where we can spend the night.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can start our research after that.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that place over there look good?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mansion!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mansion?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dusty...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the roof is intact.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be dangerous to sleep here.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's broken glass on the floor.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a place where we can sleep before it gets dark.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a floor map here.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A floor map!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and look around inside.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that dangerous?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And wouldn't the rooms be locked?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be here.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the office?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this key here?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's the master key.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be in trouble if we lost that, so we should leave it here.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That makes sense.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can enter the rooms.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:18.37,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's look for a room we can use.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:22.69,0:10:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you normally go look together?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crime is going to happen soon.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet anything on it.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He started it!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crime occurred shortly after.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find anything on your side?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine had shards from a mirror all over.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to sleep there unless we clean it up.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Mine was in a similar state.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sugimura!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:07.81,0:11:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find anything?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine was fairly clean. We might able to use it.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming down now.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kaitou-kun?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still looking?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:17.85,0:11:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, let's go find him.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reception room?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:52.30,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try the end of the hall?{Ul... I had faith in you.}
Dialogue: 9,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't open.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:10.49,0:12:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's locked.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get the master key.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Blood!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:43.91,0:12:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it takes for her to get into a movie?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, who would do this?!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be over...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the end of the footage.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:23.64,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think the culprit is?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.62,Staff Room,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(638.286,348.704)\fad(0,150)\be1\c&H091116&\b0\fs25\fscx150\fscy150\3c&H0E1423&\i0}Geshi
