Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.95,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(636,348.59)\fad(250,0)\bord1\blur3\b1\c&H030004&\fscx151\fscy156\3c&H777687&}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.95,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(636,349.733)\fad(250,0)\b1\c&H030004&\fscx151\fscy156}Hyouka
Dialogue: 9,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything to you in a minute.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, let me ask you one question.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From a technical standpoint, what do you think of this video?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:45.83,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be perfectly frank, it's crude.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:50.75,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think, too.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:52.47,0:13:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No amount of passion can overcome a lack of technical expertise.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that fine?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I also think it's fine.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Producing things solely for self-gratification is not necessarily bad.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:07.07,0:14:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's well-made or not is not particularly important.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:11.15,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you notice anything else fatal to this project?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not finished yet.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:18.39,0:14:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Thus it cannot even be called self-gratifying.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as you saw, the location is special, so it can only be filmed during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it still isn't finished.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the filming not go as planned?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:31.99,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, every deadline was met according to schedule, and the last of the filming was supposed to be next Sunday.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the problem?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The script.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:40.46,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The class asked Hongou Mayu, who had once written some comics, to write a script for an hour-long film.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongou did everything she could.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:49.61,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she fell ill after writing up to this part of the script.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're not asking us to finish it...
Dialogue: 9,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't ask that much.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going back to my first question, though:
Dialogue: 9,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think the culprit is?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:05.11,0:15:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongou fell ill just before writing the conclusion to the story.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:08.79,0:15:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The viewer should be able to identify the culprit from just these scenes.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:13.58,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But would an amateur scriptwriter put the right clues where they should be?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has studied mystery quite intensely.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:22.79,0:15:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have obeyed the Ten Commandments, Chandler's Laws, and the Twenty Rules.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moses's Ten Commandments?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Knox's Ten Commandments.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:32.27,0:15:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, Chandler's Laws, and the Twenty Rules are all rules set for writing detective fiction.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:37.61,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the key to the mystery should already be in our hands.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:41.21,0:15:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind, who do you think the culprit is?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what she meant by "good luck".
Dialogue: 9,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really say who did it.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A database can't draw any conclusions.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm not sure, myself.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:54.92,0:15:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a few things I thought were fishy.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:00.91,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking this is your kind of thing, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The role of the detective.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that face says you're not interested...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't really paying attention.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we watch it again, then?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just leave me alone?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who you think is suspicious is good enough.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me who you think the culprit is.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:19.00,0:16:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then I think it's Yamanishi-senpai.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of his attitude.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki! Use your head!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you think about it, Irisu-senpai?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with mysteries.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:38.81,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you stop them from making a mystery?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't initially part of the project.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:47.04,0:16:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only just returned from Hokkaido and took responsibility for the project two days ago.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:51.71,0:16:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have been against it had I been there initially.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then one more question:
Dialogue: 9,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose the Classics Club for this?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, because I had previously met Chitanda.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second, because I heard about Hyouka.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:11.73,0:17:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know about it?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Itoigawa-sensei tell her?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:14.97,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was first informed of the situation, you were the first to come to mind.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:19.22,0:17:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be able to play the role of detective for us.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect too much from us.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:25.27,0:17:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you'd have to go out of your way to help.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:29.79,0:17:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:31.22,0:17:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ends the screening.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:33.59,0:17:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, and good work.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:41.34,0:17:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the conclusion?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do everything I can,
Dialogue: 9,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we must present it unfinished, then so be it.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't right!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be too sad to leave the movie unfinished like this!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:59.39,0:18:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irisu obviously doesn't want that either.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:02.05,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ending it unfinished will leave a bad aftertaste.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:05.35,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Especially since everyone worked so hard.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:09.14,0:18:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:09.93,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why did Hongou-san have to stop writing the script,
Dialogue: 9,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,betraying her classmates' trust and ruining her own health?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:23.39,0:18:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we help her, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you have anything better to do.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Oreki-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In memory of Hongou-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongou isn't dead.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Oreki-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do if we can't figure out who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:43.99,0:18:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to just apologize to everyone in 2-F?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept that much responsibility.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you were to simply take on the role of observers?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observers?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:00.41,0:19:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can listen to what our class's amateur detectives have to say and offer your opinions.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:15.16,0:19:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's okay.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thank you.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irisu-senpai is pretty famous.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See over there?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:29.69,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her family runs that general hospital there.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's the princess of a large hospital?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:36.12,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all she's famous for.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a nickname.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:41.89,0:19:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think it is?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Empress".
Dialogue: 9,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a sadist?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:47.39,0:19:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be "The Queen".{totally don't get this - is a litteral TL (queen) ok?}{Never heard of "queening"? There are... okay. I'll stop here.}
Dialogue: 9,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I salute your dedication to playing the straight man.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:52.69,0:19:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are her good looks, of course, but apparently she's good at working people hard, too.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:57.23,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that those around her just end up being her pawns.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite something.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:04.01,0:20:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, since The Empress herself has graced us with her presence,
Dialogue: 9,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how about we come up with archetypes for ourselves, too?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archetypes?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, Mayaka can be Justice. {we're capitalizing so I don't think we need to quote them too}
Dialogue: 9,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of wanted to go with Judgement, though.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:18.46,0:20:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tarot cards.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, then?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say The Fool.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, maybe The Magician.{I'd say The Hierophant.}
Dialogue: 9,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Chitanda-san be The Fool.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 9,0:20:32.33,0:20:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I suppose I am The Fool.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:35.32,0:20:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it might not be a very good thing.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:38.73,0:20:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 9,0:20:39.87,0:20:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:40.72,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Oreki-san?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:41.84,0:20:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd be Strength, of course.{I'd say The Hermit.}
Dialogue: 9,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think The Star would suit him.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, definitely Strength.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fits him perfectly.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:53.46,0:20:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing that's not a compliment.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be wrong about that.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:59.06,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an annoying guy.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:19.88,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!{Girlfriending.}
Dialogue: 9,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to meet you.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:27.41,0:21:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This young lady is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:33.05,0:21:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:35.17,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:36.40,0:21:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we're meeting someone who will take us to see the detectives and hear what they have to say.{Merging lines.}
Dialogue: 9,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you arrange that?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Online.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:46.05,0:21:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chat room for students on the Kamiyama High home page.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there is?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you show me later?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:56.37,0:21:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Classics Club room?{THAT VOICE}
Dialogue: 9,0:22:01.33,0:22:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Are you from class 2-F?
Dialogue: 9,0:22:04.26,0:22:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Eba Kurako.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:06.73,0:22:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.{Answer the question!!}
Dialogue: 9,0:22:08.88,0:22:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you've already heard from Irisu, I'll be introducing you to the detectives.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:15.55,0:22:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would follow me.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those snacks, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 9,0:22:21.83,0:22:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Today I brought some chocolates I was given.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:25.89,0:22:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could share them during the discussion.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 9,0:22:31.38,0:22:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to think on an empty stomach, after all.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:35.78,0:22:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to hearing your line of thought on this, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:41.51,0:22:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you guys just having a blast.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:45.33,0:22:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, mind if I ask something?
Dialogue: 9,0:22:47.97,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:49.03,0:22:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will we be talking to?
Dialogue: 9,0:22:50.87,0:22:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assistant director, the props master, and the publicity manager.{I'm assuming 後方 means something like 後方支援 or 裏方}{広報 means publicity.}
Dialogue: 9,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what were you in charge of, Eba-san?
Dialogue: 9,0:22:58.56,0:23:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't take part in the project.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't interest me.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:03.00,0:23:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that answer.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:06.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you close to Hongou-san?{Chitanda... killing off Hongou again.}
Dialogue: 9,0:23:09.64,0:23:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 9,0:23:10.78,0:23:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious as to what kind of person wrote that script.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:21.58,0:23:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongou is...
Dialogue: 9,0:23:23.84,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,diligent, careful,
Dialogue: 9,0:23:26.13,0:23:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has a strong sense of responsibility,
Dialogue: 9,0:23:27.55,0:23:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ridiculously kind, and easily moved.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my best friend.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:36.67,0:23:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:39.51,0:23:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:40.14,0:23:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since production is on hiatus, nobody should interrupt you.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:52.82,0:23:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These three are our class's amateur detectives.
